1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Source Gate means confirmed primary material.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
A subtitle file is usable because it contains timestamped speech text.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Metadata alone cannot support speaker logic.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Therefore reports must preserve transcript evidence.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
This creates a workflow where claims remain tied to their source.
